den, PA-NJ-DE-MD]]\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"|[[Atlanta metropolitan area|Atlanta-Sandy Springs-Roswell, GA]] || 78,980 || 5,268,860 || 1.5% || style=\"text-align:left;\"|[[Atlanta metropolitan area|Atlanta\u2013Athens-Clarke County\u2013Sandy Springs, GA]]\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"|[[Greater Boston|Boston\u2013Cambridge\u2013Newton, MA-NH]] || 62,598 || 4,552,402 || 1.4% || style=\"text-align:left;\"|[[Greater Boston|Boston\u2013Worcester\u2013Providence, MA-RI-NH-CT]]\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"|[[Metro Detroit|Detroit\u2013Warren\u2013Livonia, MI]] || 55,087 || 4,296,250 || 1.3% || style=\"text-align:left;\"|[[Metro Detroit|Detroit-Warren-Ann Arbor, MI]]\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"|[[Seattle metropolitan area|Seattle\u2013Tacoma\u2013Bellevue, WA]] || 52,652 || 3,439,809 || 1.5% || style=\"text-align:left;\"|[[Seattle metropolitan area|Seattle-Tacoma, WA]]\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"|[[Miami metropolitan area|Miami\u2013Fort Lauderdale\u2013West Palm Beach, FL]] || 41,334 || 5,564,635 || 0.7% || style=\"text-align:left;\"|[[South Florida|Miami-Fort Lauderdale-Port St. Lucie, FL]]\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"|[[Baltimore metropolitan area|Baltimore\u2013Columbia\u2013Towson, MD]] || 32,193 || 2,710,489 || 1.2% || style=\"text-align:left;\"|[[Baltimore\u2013Washington metropolitan area|Washington-Baltimore-Arlington, DC-MD-VA-WV-PA]]\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"|[[Phoenix metropolitan area|Phoenix\u2013Mesa\u2013Glendale, AZ]] || 31,203 || 4,192,887 || 0.7% ||\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"|[[Minneapolis-Saint Paul|Minneapolis-St. Paul\u2013Bloomington, MN-WI]] || 29,453 || 3,279,833 || 0.9% || style=\"text-align:left;\"|[[Minneapolis\u2013Saint Paul|Minneapolis-St. Paul MN-WI]]\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"|[[Greater Orlando|Orlando\u2013Kissimmee\u2013Sanford, FL]] || 26,105 || 2,134,411 || 1.2% || style=\"text-align:left;\"|[[Central Florida|Orlando\u2013Deltona\u2013Daytona Beach, FL]]\n|-\n| style=\"text-align: