e in Gujarat, count now 53 - The Economic Times |publisher=M.economictimes.com |date=2020-03-28 |accessdate=2020-04-01}}</ref>\n*First recovery reported on 29 March, 34-year-old female from Ahmedabad. <ref>{{cite web|author=TV9 Webdesk 9 |url=https://tv9gujarati.in/first-recovery-in-gujarat-coronavirus-positive-patient-tested-negative-after-treatment-in-surat-corona-ni-dehshat-vache-sara-samachar-surat-ma-corona-no-dardi-thayo-sajo/ |title=\u0a95\u0acb\u0ab0\u0acb\u0aa8\u0abe\u0aa8\u0ac0 \u0aa6\u0ab9\u0ac7\u0ab6\u0aa4 \u0ab5\u0a9a\u0acd\u0a9a\u0ac7 \u0ab8\u0abe\u0ab0\u0abe \u0ab8\u0aae\u0abe\u0a9a\u0abe\u0ab0, \u0ab8\u0ac1\u0ab0\u0aa4\u0aae\u0abe\u0a82 \u0a95\u0acb\u0ab0\u0acb\u0aa8\u0abe\u0aa8\u0acb \u0aa6\u0ab0\u0acd\u0aa6\u0ac0 \u0aa5\u0aaf\u0acb \u0ab8\u0abe\u0a9c\u0acb |publisher=Tv9gujarati.in |date= |accessdate=2020-04-01}}</ref>\n*\n\n==Statistics==\n===Cases by district <ref>{{cite web|url=https://ingujarat.in/information/corona-virus-cases-in-gujarat-covid19/ |title=Corona virus cases in Gujarat Live tracker|date=2020-04-03 |accessdate=2020-04-03}}</ref>=== \n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders sortable citiwise-data\" style=\"text-align:right; font-size:90%; width:100px;\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" |District\n! scope=\"col\" |Confirmed cases\n!Active cases\n! scope=\"col\" |Deaths\n!Recover\n|-\n!scope=\"row\" |[[Ahmedabad district|Ahmedabad]]\n| 38\n|30\n| 3\n|5\n|-\n!scope=\"row\" |[[Vadodara district|Vadodara]]\n|9\n|6\n|1\n|1\n|-\n!scope=\"row\" |[[Rajkot district|Rajkot]]\n|10\n|9\n|0\n|1\n|-\n!scope=\"row\" |[[Surat district|Surat]]\n|12\n|8\n|1\n|3\n|-\n!scope=\"row\" |[[Gandhinagar district|Gandhinagar]]\n|11\n|11\n|0\n|0\n|-\n!scope=\"row\" |[[Gir Somnath district|Gir Somnath]]\n|2\n|2\n|0\n|0\n|-\n!scope=\"row\" |[[Kutch district|Kutch]]\n|1\n|1\n|0\n|0\n|-\n!scope=\"row\" |[[Bhavnagar district|Bhavnagar]]\n|7\n|5\n|2\n|0\n|-\n!scope=\"row\" |[[Mahesana district|Mahesana]]\n|1\n|1\n|0\n|0\n|-\n!scope=\"row\" |[[Porbandar district|Porbandar]]\n|3\n|3